{
  "info": {
    "name": "API Raízes do Nordeste",
    "_postman_id": "a1b2c3d4-e5f6-7890-1234-567890abcdef",
    "description": "Coleção de testes da API Raízes do Nordeste — Projeto Multidisciplinar UNINTER 2026.\n\n## Como usar\n\n**Pré-requisito:** ter pelo menos 1 usuário ADMIN no banco. Como criar:\n1. Suba a API e o banco\n2. Rode T01 (registra um CLIENT) e T02 (faz login)\n3. Promova esse usuário a ADMIN via Prisma Studio (`npx prisma studio`) ou seed\n4. Em **Setup → Login Admin**, ajuste email/senha e rode — preenche `adminAccessToken` automaticamente\n\n**Ordem sugerida dos testes:** Setup → Auth → Units → Products → Menu → Stock Movements\n\n## Variáveis da coleção\n- `baseUrl` (default http://localhost:8000)\n- `accessToken` — token do cliente comum (auto-salvo no T02)\n- `refreshToken` — auto-salvo no T02\n- `adminAccessToken` — token do admin (auto-salvo no Setup → Login Admin)\n- `unitId`, `productId` — auto-salvos após criação",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "baseUrl", "value": "http://localhost:8000", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "accessToken", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "refreshToken", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "adminAccessToken", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "unitId", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "productId", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "orderId", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "paidOrderId", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "refusedOrderId", "value": "", "type": "string" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Setup",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Login Admin (preenche adminAccessToken)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"admin@raizes.com\",\n  \"password\": \"Admin@123\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/login",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "login"]
            },
            "description": "Login com credenciais de admin. Ajuste email/senha para os do seu banco."
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set('adminAccessToken', json.accessToken);"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
